trans-unit.source: Provides an interface to manage a template editing area.
trans-unit.target: 템플릿 편집 영역을 관리하기 위한 인터페이스를 제공합니다.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ITemplateEditingFrame> interface is obsolete.
Use the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner.TemplateGroups%2A> property to access template groups, and template definitions within template groups, for a control designer.
trans-unit.target: 사용 하 여 <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner.TemplateGroups%2A> 템플릿 그룹 및 컨트롤 디자이너에 대 한 템플릿 그룹 내에서 템플릿 정의 액세스 하는 속성입니다.

trans-unit.source: A template editing frame represents the UI for a template editor of a templated control designer.
trans-unit.target: 템플릿 편집 프레임을 템플릿 기반 컨트롤 디자이너의 템플릿 편집기에 대 한 UI를 나타냅니다.

trans-unit.source: <see langword="true" /> if changes to the document should be saved; otherwise, <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: 문서의 변경 내용을 저장해야 하면 <see langword="true" />이고, 그렇지 않으면 <see langword="false" />입니다.

trans-unit.source: Closes the control and optionally saves any changes.
trans-unit.target: 컨트롤을 닫고 필요한 경우 변경 내용을 저장합니다.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ITemplateEditingFrame> interface is obsolete.

Use the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.TemplateGroup.GroupStyle%2A> property on each template group element in the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner.TemplateGroups%2A> collection of a control designer.
trans-unit.target: 사용 하 여는 <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.TemplateGroup.GroupStyle%2A> 각 템플릿 그룹 요소에 대해 속성은 <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner.TemplateGroups%2A> 컨트롤 디자이너의 컬렉션입니다.

trans-unit.source: Gets the style for the editing frame.
A <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Style" /> that represents the Web server control style attributes for the editing frame.
trans-unit.target: 편집 프레임의 웹 서버 컨트롤 스타일 특성을 나타내는 <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Style" />입니다.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ITemplateEditingFrame> interface is obsolete.

Use the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.TemplateGroup.GroupStyle%2A> property on each template group element in the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner.TemplateGroups%2A> collection of a control designer.
trans-unit.target: 사용 하 여는 <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.TemplateGroup.GroupStyle%2A> 각 템플릿 그룹 요소에 대해 속성은 <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner.TemplateGroups%2A> 컨트롤 디자이너의 컬렉션입니다.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the initial height of the control.
The initial height of the control.
The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ITemplateEditingFrame> interface is obsolete.

Use the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Style.Height%2A> property in the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.TemplateGroup.GroupStyle%2A> property for each template group element in the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner.TemplateGroups%2A> collection of a control designer.
trans-unit.target: 사용 하 여는 <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Style.Height%2A> 속성에는 <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.TemplateGroup.GroupStyle%2A> 의 각 서식 파일 그룹 요소에 대 한 속성의 <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner.TemplateGroups%2A> 컨트롤 디자이너의 컬렉션입니다.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the initial width of the control.
The initial width of the control.
The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ITemplateEditingFrame> interface is obsolete.

Use the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Style.Width%2A> property in the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.TemplateGroup.GroupStyle%2A> property for each template group element in the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner.TemplateGroups%2A> collection of a control designer.
trans-unit.target: 사용 하 여는 <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Style.Width%2A> 속성에는 <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.TemplateGroup.GroupStyle%2A> 의 각 서식 파일 그룹 요소에 대 한 속성의 <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner.TemplateGroups%2A> 컨트롤 디자이너의 컬렉션입니다.

trans-unit.source: Gets the name of the editing frame.
The name of the editing frame.
The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ITemplateEditingFrame> interface is obsolete.

The template group name is provided in the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.TemplateGroup.GroupName%2A> property of each template group element in the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner.TemplateGroups%2A> collection of a control designer.
trans-unit.target: 서식 파일 그룹 이름이 제공 되는 <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.TemplateGroup.GroupName%2A> 속성의 각 서식 파일 그룹 요소에는 <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner.TemplateGroups%2A> 컨트롤 디자이너의 컬렉션입니다.

trans-unit.source: Opens and displays the control.
The new width for the control.
The new height for the control.
Resizes the control to the specified width and height.
trans-unit.target: 지정된 너비와 높이로 컨트롤의 크기를 조정합니다.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ITemplateEditingFrame> interface is obsolete.

Use the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.TemplateGroup.GroupStyle%2A> property on each template group element in the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner.TemplateGroups%2A> collection of a control designer.
trans-unit.target: 사용 하 여는 <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.TemplateGroup.GroupStyle%2A> 각 템플릿 그룹 요소에 대해 속성은 <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner.TemplateGroups%2A> 컨트롤 디자이너의 컬렉션입니다.

trans-unit.source: Saves any changes to the document.
Gets a set of names of templates to use.
An array of template names.
The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ITemplateEditingFrame> interface is obsolete.
A template name is provided through the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.DesignerObject.Name%2A> property of a <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.TemplateDefinition> object.
trans-unit.target: 템플릿 이름이 통해 제공 되는 <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.DesignerObject.Name%2A> 의 속성은 <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.TemplateDefinition> 개체입니다.

trans-unit.source: Enumerate the collection of template definitions by using the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.TemplateGroup.Templates%2A> property of each <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.TemplateGroup> element in the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner.TemplateGroups%2A> collection of a control designer.
trans-unit.target: 사용 하 여 템플릿 정의의 컬렉션을 열거 하는 <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.TemplateGroup.Templates%2A> 각 속성 <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.TemplateGroup> 요소에는 <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner.TemplateGroups%2A> 컨트롤 디자이너의 컬렉션입니다.

trans-unit.source: Gets the template styles for the control.
An array of <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Style" /> objects that represent the template styles for the control.
trans-unit.target: 컨트롤의 템플릿 스타일을 나타내는 <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Style" /> 개체의 배열입니다.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ITemplateEditingFrame> interface is obsolete.
A template style is provided through the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.TemplateDefinition.Style%2A> property of a <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.TemplateDefinition> object.
trans-unit.target: 템플릿 스타일을 통해 제공 되는 <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.TemplateDefinition.Style%2A> 속성은 <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.TemplateDefinition> 개체입니다.

trans-unit.source: Enumerate the collection of template definitions by using the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.TemplateGroup.Templates%2A> property of each <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.TemplateGroup> element in the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner.TemplateGroups%2A> collection of a control designer.
trans-unit.target: 사용 하 여 템플릿 정의의 컬렉션을 열거 하는 <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.TemplateGroup.Templates%2A> 각 속성 <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.TemplateGroup> 요소에는 <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner.TemplateGroups%2A> 컨트롤 디자이너의 컬렉션입니다.

trans-unit.source: The new name for the control.
Changes the name of the control to the specified name.
The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ITemplateEditingFrame> interface is obsolete.

Use the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.TemplateGroup.GroupStyle%2A> property on each template group element in the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner.TemplateGroups%2A> collection of a control designer.
trans-unit.target: 사용 하 여는 <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.TemplateGroup.GroupStyle%2A> 각 템플릿 그룹 요소에 대해 속성은 <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner.TemplateGroups%2A> 컨트롤 디자이너의 컬렉션입니다.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the verb that invokes the template.
A <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.Design.TemplateEditingVerb" /> that invokes the template.
The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ITemplateEditingFrame> interface is obsolete.
Use the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.TemplateGroup.GroupName%2A> property of each template group in the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner.TemplateGroups%2A> collection for a control designer.
trans-unit.target: 사용 하 여는 <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.TemplateGroup.GroupName%2A> 에서 각 템플릿 그룹의 속성은 <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner.TemplateGroups%2A> 컨트롤 디자이너에 대 한 컬렉션입니다.
